OL,3,CMore than 150 guns taken off the
OL,4,Cstreets in crime crackdown
OL,6,FMore than 150 guns have been taken off
OL,7,Fthe streets of the West Midlands over
OL,8,Fthe last year, police have said.
OL,10,Fsaid shootings have fallen across the
OL,11,Fregion since a new crime unit was set
OL,12,Fup 12 months ago.
OL,14,FThe force said 152 guns were recovered
OL,15,Fby officers - an increase from 121 the
OL,16,Fprevious year.
OL,18,FLast year, there were also 92 firearms
OL,19,Fdischarges, compared to 126 the
OL,20,Fprevious year and 161 the year before.
