OL,4,Cstreets in crime crackdown
OL,6,FThe team responsible for the anti-gun
OL,7,Fwork is its major crime unit - split
OL,8,Finto proactive and reactive teams -
OL,9,Fwhich was brought in as part of a
OL,10,Fmajor reorganisation of West Midlands
OL,11,FPolice last year.
OL,13,FDetective Superintendent Scott
OL,14,FGriffiths, who oversees the teams,
OL,15,Fsaid: "We've had a really successful
OL,16,Fyear of targeting serious and
OL,17,Forganised crime in the West Midlands.
