OL,4,Cstreets in crime crackdown
OL,6,F"We've uncovered criminal gangs
OL,7,Fthrough our proactive work to seek out
OL,8,Fthose who use violence and
OL,9,Fintimidation, and when we've had major
OL,10,Fincidents that have resulted in people
OL,11,Fbeing seriously injured on the streets
OL,12,Fof the West Midlands, we've acted
OL,13,Fswiftly and decisively to investigate
OL,14,Fand put those responsible behind bars
OL,15,Ffor years to come."
OL,17,FThe figures also revealed that one of
OL,18,Fthe six reactive teams alone charged
OL,19,Fmore than 50 people in the last year,
OL,20,Fincluding 21 for attempted murder.
