OL,6,FMr Griffiths added: "The new way of
OL,7,Fworking which came into place at the
OL,8,Fstart of last year means we've got
OL,9,Fdedicated resources to quickly review
OL,10,FCCTV, mobile phone and forensic
OL,11,Fevidence.
OL,13,F"But we're also working really closely
OL,14,Fwith local policing areas to
OL,15,Funderstand the community impact and
OL,16,Fgather information and intelligence."
